@startuml ComponentRegistry_CompositeCatalog
!theme plain
left to right direction
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam nodesep 70
skinparam ranksep 70

skinparam package {
    BorderColor #455A64
    FontStyle bold
}

skinparam class {
    BorderColor #424242
    BackgroundColor #FAFAFA
    BackgroundColor<<User>> #FFF3E0
    BackgroundColor<<Config>> #E3F2FD
    BackgroundColor<<Registry>> #F3E5F5
    BackgroundColor<<Catalog>> #E8F5E9
    BackgroundColor<<Upstream>> #ECEFF1
    BackgroundColor<<Product>> #FFF8E1
}

skinparam note {
    BackgroundColor #FFFDE7
    BorderColor #F9A825
    FontSize 10
}

title ComponentRegistry + CompositeCatalog 组件注册与装配流程

actor "用户代码" as User

package "1. 用户自定义组件" {
    class UserEncoderBuilder <<User>> {
        + decorator: register_encoder(my_encoder)
        + build(obs_space, action_space, model_config, framework)
    }

    class UserActorHeadBuilder <<User>> {
        + decorator: register_actor_head(my_actor_head)
        + build(latent_dims, action_space, model_config, framework)
    }

    class UserValueHeadBuilder <<User>> {
        + decorator: register_critic_head / register_q_head / register_vf_head
        + build(latent_dims, ..., model_config, framework)
    }
}

package "2. rlframework.models.catalog" {
    class ComponentRegistry <<Registry>> {
        {static} _encoders: dict[str, EncoderBuilder]
        {static} _actor_heads: dict[str, HeadBuilder]
        {static} _critic_heads: dict[str, HeadBuilder]
        {static} _q_heads: dict[str, HeadBuilder]
        {static} _vf_heads: dict[str, HeadBuilder]
        {static} _action_dists: dict[str, Callable]
        --
        {static} register_encoder(name)
        {static} register_actor_head(name)
        {static} register_critic_head(name)
        {static} register_q_head(name)
        {static} register_vf_head(name)
        {static} register_action_dist(name)
        --
        {static} get_encoder(name)
        {static} get_actor_head(name)
        {static} get_critic_head(name)
        {static} get_q_head(name)
        {static} get_vf_head(name)
        {static} get_action_dist(name)
    }

    class PPOCompositeCatalog <<Catalog>> {
        - _framework_custom_config
        + build_actor_critic_encoder(framework)
        + build_pi_head(framework)
        + build_vf_head(framework)
    }

    class SACCompositeCatalog <<Catalog>> {
        - _framework_custom_config
        + build_encoder(framework)
        + build_pi_head(framework)
        + build_qf_head(framework)
    }

    class DQNCompositeCatalog <<Catalog>> {
        - _framework_custom_config
        + build_encoder(framework)
        + build_af_head(framework)
        + build_vf_head(framework)
    }
}

package "3. rlframework.algorithms 配置入口" {
    class CustomPPOConfig <<Config>> {
        + framework_models(encoder, actor_head, critic_head)
    }

    class CustomSACConfig <<Config>> {
        + framework_models(encoder, actor_head, critic_head, q_head)
    }
}

package "4. RLlib 原生构建链路" {
    class RLModuleSpec <<Upstream>> {
        + catalog_class
        + model_config
    }

    class PPOCatalog <<Upstream>>
    class SACCatalog <<Upstream>>
    class DQNCatalog <<Upstream>>

    class RLModule <<Upstream>> {
        + role: RLModule / Learner
        + catalog.build_*()
    }
}

package "5. 最终网络组件" {
    class CustomComponent <<Product>> {
        + 自定义 Encoder / Head 实例
    }
    class DefaultComponent <<Product>> {
        + RLlib 默认 Encoder / Head 实例
    }
}

User --> UserEncoderBuilder : 定义 builder
User --> UserActorHeadBuilder : 定义 builder
User --> UserValueHeadBuilder : 定义 builder

UserEncoderBuilder ..> ComponentRegistry : 装饰器注册\nname -> builder
UserActorHeadBuilder ..> ComponentRegistry : 装饰器注册\nname -> builder
UserValueHeadBuilder ..> ComponentRegistry : 装饰器注册\nname -> builder

User --> CustomPPOConfig : .framework_models(...)
User --> CustomSACConfig : .framework_models(...)

CustomPPOConfig ..> RLModuleSpec : catalog_class=PPOCompositeCatalog\nmodel_config._framework_custom_config
CustomSACConfig ..> RLModuleSpec : catalog_class=SACCompositeCatalog\nmodel_config._framework_custom_config

PPOCompositeCatalog --|> PPOCatalog
SACCompositeCatalog --|> SACCatalog
DQNCompositeCatalog --|> DQNCatalog

RLModuleSpec --> PPOCompositeCatalog : PPO 场景实例化
RLModuleSpec --> SACCompositeCatalog : SAC 场景实例化
RLModule --> PPOCompositeCatalog : build_actor_critic_encoder()\nbuild_pi_head() / build_vf_head()
RLModule --> SACCompositeCatalog : build_encoder()\nbuild_pi_head() / build_qf_head()
RLModule --> DQNCompositeCatalog : build_encoder()\nbuild_af_head() / build_vf_head()

PPOCompositeCatalog ..> ComponentRegistry : get_encoder()\nget_actor_head()\nget_critic_head()
SACCompositeCatalog ..> ComponentRegistry : get_encoder()\nget_actor_head()\nget_q_head()
DQNCompositeCatalog ..> ComponentRegistry : get_encoder()\nget_q_head()\nget_vf_head()

PPOCompositeCatalog --> CustomComponent : 找到 builder 后调用
SACCompositeCatalog --> CustomComponent : 找到 builder 后调用
DQNCompositeCatalog --> CustomComponent : 找到 builder 后调用
PPOCatalog --> DefaultComponent : fallback super().build_*()
SACCatalog --> DefaultComponent : fallback super().build_*()
DQNCatalog --> DefaultComponent : fallback super().build_*()
PPOCompositeCatalog ..> PPOCatalog : name=default 或未注册\n走默认实现
SACCompositeCatalog ..> SACCatalog : name=default 或未注册\n走默认实现
DQNCompositeCatalog ..> DQNCatalog : name=default 或未注册\n走默认实现

note bottom of ComponentRegistry
    ComponentRegistry 负责“名字 -> builder”的全局注册和查找。
    encoder / actor_head / critic_head 同时写入 _registered_builders，
    便于跨进程场景复用已注册 builder。
end note

note bottom of RLModuleSpec
    framework_models(...) 不直接创建网络，
    只把自定义组件名放入 model_config._framework_custom_config，
    并把 RLModuleSpec.catalog_class 切到对应 CompositeCatalog。
end note

note bottom of CustomComponent
    CompositeCatalog 的核心分支：
    1. 从 _framework_custom_config 取 custom_* 名称；
    2. 到 ComponentRegistry 查 builder；
    3. 找到则 builder(...) 创建自定义组件；
    4. 找不到或 default 则调用 RLlib 原生 Catalog。
end note

legend right
    <b>常用路径</b>
    用户注册 builder -> framework_models 选择组件 -> RLModuleSpec 使用 CompositeCatalog -> build_* 时按名称查表 -> 自定义组件或默认组件
endlegend

@enduml
